## Note on data vs. code

This MIT license applies to the **code** in this repository (CLI, skills,
recipes, schemas, tests, docs). It does NOT relicense any third-party data
retrieved from the Cortellis / Clarivate APIs.

Cortellis-derived *raw* data (anything under `raw/`, CSVs pulled directly
from the API, and API responses cached in `*.meta.json`) remains governed by
the subscriber's Cortellis / Clarivate subscription agreement and must be
handled according to that agreement.

*Derived analytical outputs* (e.g., `strategic_briefing.md`,
`scenario_library.md`, CPI rankings, mechanism crowding indices, report.md)
may be shared with third parties subject to the TOS answer recorded in
`cli_anything/cortellis/skills/landscape/docs/tos_check.md`.
